<div class="title">The Cactus That Was Too Long</div>
<div class="substance">Cacti - T. peruvianus</div>
<div class="author">by <a href="/experiences/exp.cgi?A=Search&AuthorSearch=legit_water&Exact=1">legit_water</a></div>


<div class="ts-citation">Citation:&nbsp;&nbsp; legit_water. "The Cactus That Was Too Long: An Experience with Cacti - T. peruvianus (exp22323)". <u>Erowid.org</u>. Oct 13, 2004. erowid.org/exp/22323</div>

<br/>



<div class="report-text-surround">
<table cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" align="right" border="0">
